In today's fast-paced world, the contentious issue regarding technology has ignited considerable altercation due to its profound impact on individuals and society. I firmly advocate that education is essential. However, everything is a double-edged sword, including innovation.
From my perspective, both the innumerate merits and demerits of this topic deserve thorough examination.

On the one hand, a significant advantage of technology is that it improves communication. For instance, people can connect across the globe. On the other hand, a manifest drawback of screen time should not be neglected is that it affects health.

In a nutshell, every coin has two sides. While technology offers notable advantages, its disadvantages must not be ignored. A balanced approach is essential to maximize benefits while minimizing drawbacks.

